<div class='toload proposition'>
	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Proposition 1.7.20</span>
	Given an invariant mean $\mu$ on a Boolean inverse semigroup $S$, $d_\mu$ is a metric if and only if $\mu$ is faithful.
	</p>
</div>